  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "02cf9fca4b7687de8f86ba3d6f1fdc645e5a53e7e77b72c92afdc9011942cf22": "Hello there, [?]. Akrisae was hoping to speak with you.",
    "07603bd74cb02721be6031d4339615ddfb8d1970654f102be1ca99ad9617a00d": "Hello again, [?]. You'll need to take a snapdragon seed to Betty in Port Sarim. I can teleport you there if you wish.",
    "33ea9e658b0ac4bbefc6ea960af2af3457870c42d546fcc1160abdfbac33778f": "[?], you must return to the temple below Lumbridge! Idria and her Guardians of Armadyl have already departed to support you!",
    "3690ec1d695ddf8246c348858a9353c29a0ccd5c4bc265066a0dd59971b59445": "Hello again, [?]. Any luck with that snapdragon seed?",
    "36c16a0d573e2e275ab54c20b759dd6d2568e1fe2cbdfcad88730542c3feabec": "Hello again, [?]. I imagine that snapdragon seed will have grown by now.",
    "428983892463be2582068f6fd714056155938b5c664d46f7f189c53a48133322": "Ah, [?], it's good to see you again.",
    "4b9a9d494917e22ec73010c85b7fcb9c58966977ac97c692b1f18086bed78391": "Welcome back, [?]. What news do you have?",
    "524ce46134aa96f5747610589ef662560ec9645c577250cd414b99dba86d7505": "Ah, there you are, [?]. Idria told us what happened at McGrubor's Wood. I'm glad to see you made it here safely. Now, allow me to introduce Akrisae Kolluym of the Temple Knights.",
    "66f1dfd928fbde88809fff3691721462f8ae5dac84f8fbc64c52b92db25d1142": "A Guthixian temple? This is concerning, [?]. You'd better get back there as soon as possible.",
    "68061acb1842e2567585820d4bc2cfe4d8a51d9d52aa69f81dd0889545940f3b": "Anyway, now that we're all here, I think it's time we discussed the contents of the notes that [?] found. To put it bluntly, these notes confirm all of our worst fears.",
    "6a706723e08bfeb18137a0ae71102cb10d02042ee7c0a4d8e81731defd0b668a": "Excellent work, [?]. These notes are very useful, albeit rather concerning as well. I'll let you keep hold of them. You'll probably want to read them yourself, if you haven't already.",
    "6db49e8d6873a959e3099874d3c8262f68e3971239bda2a7b65c9bd2773f64ee": "Hello again, [?]. I imagine that snapdragon seed will have grown by now. You should head on up and check on it.",
    "773d56bf81c51b89f32308eb07302a060b3973f9f3f2763eaa7c22c0f6be12a0": "Hello again, [?]. You'll need to take a snapdragon seed to Betty in Port Sarim. I have one here if needed. I can also teleport you to Port Sarim if you wish.",
    "846deb71f47287c325dd8363892d4f7e137cd358fec75f7e13ca0b0464abd390": "Any luck with the spy, [?]?",
    "85fe3dc4a5b75aa01483ed310503b0c9639b35dd6e460cf20932719611048446": "Good luck, [?].",
    "8fdf4d8f9ec34ab8b8d9defdcbe905dfad3e6878d944f3565f3d23f6921fca12": "Good to see you, [?]. How are things going?",
    "958e313c0478ac4c93884ba6e9a0d6dd692598b8e03ffa3cffeb4551b2f31a54": "Hello, [?]. How are things going?",
    "9d603bbe50925d86c75b2606ecd8820c582c37cc1cb7abaaeee96aef5c377533": "You'd better get back there as soon as possible, [?]. We can't let Movario find the Stone.",
    "9f936939407806f49a347350e98d36fb99e841f03b0913889bfbc1ad6193b475": "Hello there, [?]. If you need a hand with anything, you should talk to Akrisae.",
